<div class='mailer__content'>
  <p class='govuk-body'>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
  <p class='govuk-body'>It's great you've enrolled on the <%= @programme.title %> programme!</p>
  <p class='govuk-body'>If you want to start with an online course, <%= link_to 'find one here and sign up', courses_url(location: 'Online', certificate: @programme.slug) %></p>
  <p class='govuk-body'>You'll also need to do some mentored learning, so checkout some of our <%= link_to 'available courses and dates', courses_url(location: 'Face to face', certificate: @programme.slug) %></p>
  <p class='govuk-body'>We look forward to seeing your progress soon!</p>
  <p class='govuk-body'>The NCCE Team</p>
</div>
